TERMS OF RESPONSIBILITY
===============

Purpose: To briefly suggest responsibilities for the user 
using this software.

First off, as a developer, thank you for using this extension. 
I hope you will find Chronos useful in your browsing experience.

As a user of this extension, you are free to use this software 
however you like. However, Chronos is designed to manage your
web browsing productivity in a specific manner, which will 
require some cooperation from the user's side in order for it to 
function effectively.

